  "body": "<!--NOTE: -->\r\n<!--- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nAt least here\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/c12dc8aa980e26399ffceeebe7e6a56048d7f0bd/packages/lodestar/src/api/impl/beacon/state/index.ts#L77-L79\r\n\r\nThis call triggers an expensive loop that is not really used in practice. Also related https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/3683\r\n\r\nCalling any API endpoint should require limited resources to process to prevent DOS vectors. Expensive calls should only be possible under some flag like `--enable-debug-routes`\r\n\r\n",
